abstracts.cdata!:
The Highway Maintenance Project will
            assist in financing: (i) highway maintenance equipment and
            spare parts required for the maintenance of 3,900 km of
            roads; (ii) technical assistance; (iii) feasibility study
            and detailed engineering of the Bengui-Bossembele road.
